properties.headline: Gale Warning issued February 11 at 3:56AM EST until February 12 at 9:00AM EST by NWS Boston/Norton MA
properties.description:
* WHAT...Northwest winds 15 to 25 kt with gusts up to 35 kt and
seas 5 to 8 feet expected.

* WHERE...Coastal waters from Provincetown MA to Chatham MA to
Nantucket MA out 20 nm.

* WHEN...From 1 AM to 9 AM EST Wednesday.

* IMPACTS...Strong winds will cause hazardous seas which could
capsize or damage vessels and reduce visibility.
properties.instruction:
Mariners should alter plans to avoid these hazardous conditions.
Remain in port, seek safe harbor, alter course, and/or secure the
vessel for severe conditions.

NWSheadline: GALE WARNING IN EFFECT FROM 1 AM TO 9 AM EST WEDNESDAY... ...SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IS CANCELLED
